  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Ellicott's Commentary for English Readers",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(16) The words, “and sought to slay Him,” should be omitted. They have been inserted in some MSS. to explain the first clause of ",
