        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Olshausen and de Wette import this in the words: “As in God rest and action are united, so in Christ are contemplation and activity.” But there is no mention of rest and contemplation. According to Godet, Jesus says, “",
        "children": []
      },
