        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἓως ἄρτι",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " carries our view of God’s working, which began with the creation, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "onwards to the present moment",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the moment wherein Jesus has to defend Himself on account of Sabbath-breaking. In conformity with this redemptive work of God the Father onwards until now, and which was interrupted by no rest, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "He",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " also works. The inference that herein is implied a divine ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
