        "text": "ὅτι ταῦτα ἐποίει ἐν σαββάτῳ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The plural and the imperfect show that the cure of the impotent man was not the only case they had in view. Their allies in the provinces had made them acquainted with similar cases. It would almost seem as if He was in the habit of thus signalising the Sabbath.",
        "children": []
